{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f01f794cdd","title":"谢富治在市革委会上的讲话","origin":"《北京大学文革资料选编（下）》，美国华忆出版社，2020。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"abc94416a8","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":26,"articleId":"f01f794cdd"}],"tags":[{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d82da26cbe","type":"title","text":"谢富治在市革委会上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"3eda1bc5ef","type":"paragraph","text":"谢副总理问：北大开学了没有？ 聂元梓：开了，是二十五日开的。 谢问师大：师大开学了没有？","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"9a0fb2475b","type":"paragraph","text":"谭厚兰：开学了。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"67b38b1492","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：到底有几个学校开学了？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"e1deabeea7","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：听今天早晨中央广播电台广播的是 11 个学校，没有北大。 谢：那可能是老稿子吧。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"e30c70d92c","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：可能。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"fc6159379e","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：今天几号了？（聂：27 号）","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"aa68647cfe","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：今天批的文件都写上二十九日了。整天不睡觉，糊里糊涂的，不知是几号了。要把今天签字的文件都改成二十七号（让秘书）。夜里不睡觉非常忙，十二个省的代表都要来，给他们谈问题，石家庄有一个什么演出团。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"098441ba99","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：有一个。天津还有一个是红代会的。已经告诉他们让他们回来了，通知一定都叫回来。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"fe0ada3e6b","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：北航是不是开学了？开课了没有？伯达同志昨天还在问呢，伯达同志说，先在你们学校试的点，你们要开课。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"19f7b4fb89","type":"paragraph","text":"北航代表：开了。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"073eb34250","type":"paragraph","text":"聂：我们这里没有联合起来，校文革领导开学了。我们希望井冈山的同志一块开课。今天我们发了一个声明，希望在开课领导小组的班子里井冈山的同志也参加进来。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"},{"id":"5fae072880","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：这很好！","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd"}],"page":{"id":"7a36416659","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f01f794cdd","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}